---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Scholarships - ECEA"
  description="The East Coast Enduro Association awards scholarships in memory of Skip Stoner and Mike Little to recognize achievement and support the educational goals of ECEA members."
>
  <PageHeader
    title="ECEA Scholarships"
    subtitle="Investing in the Next Generation of Riders"
  />

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Each year, the East Coast Enduro Association awards scholarships to recognize achievement by ECEA members. We are proud to offer two annual scholarships named in honor of two individuals who gave so much to our community.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Applications and all supporting documents must be emailed or submitted no later than <strong>August 31, 2026</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skip Stoner Scholarship -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">2026 ECEA Skip Stoner Memorial Scholarship Program</h2>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-6">Up to two $500 scholarships available</p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Each year, the East Coast Enduro Association (ECEA) will award up to two $500 scholarships to recognize achievement by an ECEA member in Skip Stoner's memory. Skip was a mentor to many kids over the years. He and his family would open their shop, home, and hearts to help others. In return we are honored to present an annual scholarship in his name.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">All applicants for these scholarships:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>Must be an <strong>immediate ECEA club family member</strong> e.g. self, spouse, or child of; and</li>
            <li>Must be pursuing or planning to earn a degree and/or certification at an <strong>institution, trade, or technical school</strong> in the 2026–2027 scholastic year; and</li>
            <li>
              Must be a current competitor or have an immediate ECEA family member (in good standing) who has also participated in at least <strong>25% of the events</strong> run in either the 2025 ECEA Enduro Series and/or Hare Scrambles Series — <strong>OR</strong> — an active participating member in an ECEA Club or ECEA Committee.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
            <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800">2026 Deadline: August 31, 2026</p>
            <p class="text-amber-700 text-sm mt-1">Scholarship applications and supporting documents must be emailed or submitted no later than August 31, 2026.</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Required Documentation</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Letters of Recommendation</p>
              <p>Two letters of recommendation are required. One shall be from your ECEA club's president (if applicable) and/or the others should be from a worthy individual who can describe your participation and/or involvement within the ECEA community. They may mail or email their letters to the ECEA Scholarship Committee via <a href="mailto:ecea.secy@verizon.net" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">ecea.secy@verizon.net</a> or you can upload them with your application submission.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Proof of Enrollment</p>
              <p>Proof of Enrollment as a student in a post secondary institution. This can be a paid tuition bill or a schedule showing semester dates. Please upload or send to: <a href="mailto:ecea.secy@verizon.net" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">ecea.secy@verizon.net</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSegLGs0rZBxa7J2QJ7X_HJGdd-zPBnNiAs4Rq5KN3ikvEqUrw/viewform"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Apply for the Skip Stoner Scholarship
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <img
            src="/uploads/scholarships/ss-scholarship-flyer.png"
            alt="2026 Skip Stoner Memorial Scholarship Flyer"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mike Little Scholarship -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/uploads/scholarships/ml-scholarship-flyer.png"
            alt="2026 Mike Little Memorial Scholarship Flyer"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">2026 ECEA Mike Little Memorial Scholarship Program</h2>
          <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-6">Up to two $500 scholarships available</p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Each year, the ECEA will award up to two $500 scholarships to recognize achievement by ECEA members in our past ECEA officer, Mike Little's memory. Mike always felt deeply about the youth in our series. In return we are honored to present an annual scholarship in his name.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">All applicants for these scholarships:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-outside ml-5 space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>Must be an <strong>ECEA club member</strong>; and</li>
            <li>
              Must be pursuing or planning to pursue a <strong>full-time post-secondary course of study</strong> in a degree/certification program at a United States college/institution in the 2026–2027 scholastic year or employed full-time while attending school part-time; and
            </li>
            <li>
              Must have participated in at least <strong>25% of the events</strong> run in either the 2025 ECEA Enduro Series and/or Hare Scrambles Series or an active participating member of their ECEA club or an ECEA Committee.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
            <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800">2026 Deadline: August 31, 2026</p>
            <p class="text-amber-700 text-sm mt-1">Scholarship applications and supporting documents must be emailed or submitted no later than August 31, 2026.</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Required Documentation</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Letters of Recommendation</p>
              <p>Two letters of recommendation are required. One shall be from your ECEA club's president and the other should be from a worthy individual who can describe your participation and/or involvement within the ECEA community. They may mail or email their letters to the ECEA Scholarship Committee via <a href="mailto:ecea.secy@verizon.net" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">ecea.secy@verizon.net</a>.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Proof of Enrollment</p>
              <p>Proof of Enrollment as a student in a post secondary institution. This can be a paid tuition bill or a schedule showing semester dates. Please send to: <a href="mailto:ecea.secy@verizon.net" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">ecea.secy@verizon.net</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a
            href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewDA_sbkkwTHwOgpPB2XS2K1p7XmuXNgF5YdGP0khgmlk9NA/viewform"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Apply for the Mike Little Scholarship
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Questions?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Contact the ECEA Scholarship Committee at <a href="mailto:ecea.secy@verizon.net" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">ecea.secy@verizon.net</a>. All applications and supporting documents must be submitted no later than <strong>August 31, 2026</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSegLGs0rZBxa7J2QJ7X_HJGdd-zPBnNiAs4Rq5KN3ikvEqUrw/viewform"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Apply: Skip Stoner Scholarship
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewDA_sbkkwTHwOgpPB2XS2K1p7XmuXNgF5YdGP0khgmlk9NA/viewform"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-primary-600 bg-white border border-primary-600 rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-primary-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Apply: Mike Little Scholarship
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
